entities.name: Farcaster
entities.description: A decentralized social graph protocol aiming to connect all social applications. It uses a globally unique username system, and its protocol allows for open, permissionless, and decentralized social applications.

entities.name: ElizaOS
entities.description: An AI operating system designed to build and deploy AI agents. It emphasizes modularity, scalability, and an extensible agent framework with a robust plugin ecosystem.

entities.name: GitHub
entities.description: A web-based platform and repository hosting service that provides distributed version control. It is used for code collaboration, project management, and software development.

entities.name: PostgreSQL
entities.description: A free and open-source relational database management system emphasizing extensibility and SQL compliance. It is known for its robustness, feature set, and performance.

entities.name: Anthropic
entities.description: An AI safety and research company focused on building reliable, interpretable, and steerable AI systems. They are known for developing large language models and AI research.

entities.name: Clank Tank
entities.description: A conceptual AI-powered show where AI agents could invest in projects, discussed as part of AI streaming development.

entities.name: Sourcegraph
entities.description: A code intelligence platform that helps developers search, navigate, and understand large codebases. It provides tools for code search, code browsing, and code understanding.
